prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor illustration of a slightly frazzled, but happy, cartoon sloth wearing a tiny party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch. The sloth is holding a single, very slowly melting birthday candle with a tiny flame. Below the branch, in the center of the card, is elegant, readable handwritten cursive script that reads: "Don't worry, you're not getting older... you're just taking the scenic route." The artwork is flat 2D, with soft, flowing watercolor textures, visible paper grain, artistic brush strokes, and gentle paint bleeds in pastel greens, browns, and blues.
